Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:34.64,top,Lady-in-Waiting 1,0,0,0,,How dare you try to feed Lady Lihua such lowly food!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:35.49,Fiction_Disclaimer,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(277,260)\blur1}This story is a work of fiction. The names of all of the characters, organizations, and so on are imaginary. It also bears no connection to any specific real-life events.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.64,0:01:39.10,top,Lady-in-Waiting 2,0,0,0,,Only the most luxurious foods suit our Lady Lihua.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.10,0:01:42.81,top,Lady-in-Waiting 2,0,0,0,,I'd hesitate to even {\i1}show{\i0} this to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.70,0:01:43.66,Ep_Title,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(430,470)\blur1\fs18\fsp-0.5\pos(599,304)}Episode 4: The Threat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.81,0:01:45.83,top,Lady-in-Waiting 1,0,0,0,,Who would ever think Lady Lihua would enjoy something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:49.53,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Yikes. What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.83,0:01:50.16,top,Lady-in-Waiting 2,0,0,0,,We know best what Lady Lihua likes to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.53,0:01:53.56,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,I'd never have come to the Crystal Pavilion if I'd had a choice, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:53.56,top,Lady-in-Waiting 2,0,0,0,,How dare you try to sneak this past us, servant. Shame on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.14,0:01:59.80,italics,Narrator,0,0,0,,The night the emperor visited the Jade Pavilion...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:24.78,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,There is no poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.71,0:02:29.37,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:32.08,Default,Emperor,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:36.09,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Uh-oh, the emperor directly addressed me for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.61,0:02:39.72,Default,Emperor,0,0,0,,I have a request for the famous apothecary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.07,0:02:43.30,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Famous? I have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:44.31,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.75,0:02:48.87,Default,Emperor,0,0,0,,Concubine Lihua is not well. Could you look after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.43,0:02:53.52,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,By "look after her," he means "cure her."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:57.58,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,The word of the emperor is the word of the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:03:00.07,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,If I declined, that would be grounds for my beheading.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:01.53,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Yes, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:08.28,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Why would he say that in front of another concubine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.28,0:03:12.92,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,His Majesty really is "an emperor" by nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:18.17,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,That said, it's pretty incredible that they treat me like this. I'm here by imperial order.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:24.76,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Since they serve Lady Lihua, I suppose they hate me as a servant of Lady Gyokuyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:25.64,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:28.22,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 1,0,0,0,,Get out if you're done cleaning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.59,0:03:30.52,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Boing boing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.28,0:03:34.61,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Oh, well. Guess I have to cook it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:39.21,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,Maomao, are you at the Crystal Pavilion now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:41.82,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm looking after Lady Lihua.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:46.08,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,I see. Lady Lihua hasn't recovered yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:49.72,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,The whitening powder's poison must still be in her system.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:54.49,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,The poisonous powder, huh? I heard it was banned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:59.53,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,I heard the eunuchs took away all the remaining powder in the rear palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:01.88,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,I see. Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:08.60,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,But a request from the emperor? You're awesome, Maomao. I was surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.24,0:04:14.60,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,He must really not trust the doctor to rely on a girl like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:17.68,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,Maomao, you're going to the kitchen later, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:18.87,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.87,0:04:20.80,Default,Xiaolan,0,0,0,,Good luck with the cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:21.88,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:27.12,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:32.90,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,In looking after Lady Lihua, the first thing I set out to do was to improve her diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:32.64,top,Maomao,0,0,0,,Um, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:33.45,top,Cook,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:35.94,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,First I needed to expel the poison still in her body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:39.12,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,To do this, a porridge with lots of fiber,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:41.58,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,plus a diuretic tea sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:45.09,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Not this. Not this either. This one...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:48.89,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,And this one, too. But not this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:53.35,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 1,0,0,0,,Enough is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:56.48,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 1,0,0,0,,This is no place for lowly girls like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:04:58.87,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Boing boing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:01.11,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,This is going to take a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:04.36,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,In that case, let's try...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.36,0:05:06.20,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,This one, that one, the other one, and this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:12.67,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 3,0,0,0,,How many times do I have to tell you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.67,0:05:15.63,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Well, first, she needs to eat something easy to digest—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:21.30,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 1,0,0,0,,No way! Sick people need {\i1}nutritious{\i0} food, not cheap stuff like that. Obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:24.59,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,So that's her usual meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:27.22,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Sure, it's nutritious,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:30.48,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,but it's too heavy for a sick person's weakened stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:33.22,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,That's not hard to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:35.06,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Why won't anyone stop them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:39.54,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 1,0,0,0,,Lady Lihua, your meal is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.12,0:05:44.76,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 1,0,0,0,,We brought you all the things you like. Please try to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.02,0:05:51.13,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 1,0,0,0,,Lady Lihua?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.13,0:05:52.75,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 2,0,0,0,,Oh no, what do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:54.06,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 1,0,0,0,,Quick, bring water!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.06,0:05:55.80,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 3,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Lady Lihua?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:58.82,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 1,0,0,0,,Lady Lihua, please have some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:04.92,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 4,0,0,0,,This is your fault, lowly servant!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:06.70,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 5,0,0,0,,Your presence ruins the atmosphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.70,0:06:07.76,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 6,0,0,0,,Get out! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:11.24,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Boing boing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:15.85,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,I won't even be able to get near her at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:19.40,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Now, what shall I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:26.49,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,If I could at least do an examination...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:31.38,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 1,0,0,0,,No need. What if you make things worse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.92,0:06:35.91,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,At that rate, she's bound to wither and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:38.73,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,People die unless they eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.10,0:06:44.46,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,She probably lost the will to live after losing her child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:52.55,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,How many days do I have left,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:56.79,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,before my head bids farewell to my body for defying the emperor's order?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.72,0:06:59.77,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,It seems like you're in a bit of a bind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.82,0:07:03.92,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Does it appear that way to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.92,0:07:05.56,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,It does appear that way to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.85,0:07:08.34,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 1,0,0,0,,Master Jinshi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:11.44,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 4,0,0,0,,What's with that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.44,0:07:12.95,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 5,0,0,0,,Why is she with Master Jinshi...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:15.08,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,An annoying misunderstanding...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:20.75,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,Let's go inside, for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:23.13,top,Lady-in-Waiting 2,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:24.25,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 1,0,0,0,,M-Master Jinshi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:24.25,top,Lady-in-Waiting 4 & 5,0,0,0,,Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:27.69,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,It's not befitting of beautiful and talented ladies like you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:30.59,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,to ignore the emperor's arrangements.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:34.57,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 1,0,0,0,,Oh! Oh no, we aren't ignoring...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.80,0:07:35.71,top,Lady-in-Waiting 4,0,0,0,,Whoa! Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:37.14,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 2,0,0,0,,Right. We were just, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.71,0:07:36.75,top,Lady-in-Waiting 5,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:40.49,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,It's scary how women can change so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:49.77,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,There. Now go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:22.27,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,She does have the will to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:26.65,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,But she's weaker than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:28.36,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Maybe she can handle rice water instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.48,0:08:34.26,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.97,0:08:38.15,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,The same shade as before...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:09:00.60,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Are you the one in charge of the concubine's makeup?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:01.94,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 1,0,0,0,,Indeed I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.47,0:09:05.31,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 1,0,0,0,,We want Lady Lihua to always be beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.72,0:09:07.99,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 1,0,0,0,,That is our duty as ladies-in-waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:11.78,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 2,0,0,0,,It's all for Lady Lihua. Obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:12.44,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:15.99,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 1,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:18.87,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Huh? Just punishing an idiot, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:22.98,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 1,0,0,0,,Ouch! You're hurting me! Stop! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.72,0:09:34.59,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,The poison will infect your whole body after a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:38.39,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,You should be glad. You'll be pretty too,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:41.16,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,just like your beloved Lady Lihua.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:48.56,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Pale, bloodless skin, sunken eye sockets, a body unable to even eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.97,0:09:52.61,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Don't you understand why this stuff was banned?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:06.11,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 1,0,0,0,,I j-just thought it would make Lady Lihua happy—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:08.68,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,I told you, it's {\i1}poison{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:12.99,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,There are no thoughts in your head. You just think you know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:17.09,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Who would be happy poisoned with the same thing that killed their son?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.73,0:10:32.79,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Go rinse your mouth and wash your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:37.51,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Hey! This is bad for the patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:39.37,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Clean this floor up immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.37,0:10:40.95,Default,Ladies-in-Waiting,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.90,0:10:47.80,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,It truly {\i1}is{\i0} scary, how women can change so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:50.23,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:55.00,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,I've really done it now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:56.02,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 2,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:11:02.70,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Lady Lihua's health was worse than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:06.11,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,I started by changing from porridge to rice water.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.11,0:11:10.89,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,I forced the food into her mouth and had her swallow slowly, repeatedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.07,0:11:15.90,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,No sense in worrying about manners at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.14,0:11:22.16,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,I did some ventilation, which thinned out the incense, revealing the smell of the sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:25.88,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Those incompetent fools can't even wipe down their mistress properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:28.08,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,How do they even call themselves ladies-in-waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:32.14,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,There's so much they could have been doing before worrying about incense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.77,0:11:37.84,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Hey. Hot water and cloth, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:39.13,Default,Ladies-in-Waiting 2 & 3,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:42.99,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,You all, get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:44.05,Default,Ladies-in-Waiting 4; 5; 6,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.16,0:11:52.54,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,I had her drink tea every chance I could find.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:56.77,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Frequent urination helps flush the poison out of her body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:12:00.28,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 2,0,0,0,,Um, are you sure Lady Lihua isn't in pain...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:02.15,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter, she must drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.35,0:12:08.00,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,She began to eat more, so I increased the amount of rice grains in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:13.00,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,When she began to be able to swallow them, I added soup and ground fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:18.63,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,I heard the lady-in-waiting was put in confinement.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.59,0:12:23.76,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Apparently, she'd hid the powder for Lady Lihua.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:29.48,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,The eunuch who was supposed to recover the powder was punished by flagellation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:48.49,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,You seem tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.27,0:12:52.44,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Yes. Unlike a certain someone, I'm quite busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:54.38,Default,Gaoshun,0,0,0,,We brought gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.60,0:12:59.30,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:02.30,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:04.64,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,He really knows what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.64,0:13:08.03,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,It's considerate people like him who become good husbands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:09.40,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,He is a eunuch, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.32,0:13:12.97,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Compared to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:20.11,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,Do you need help with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:21.72,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:25.66,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,What is it? Tell me anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:30.74,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,Over there, they need help. Someone please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:33.44,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,Everyone, please hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.44,0:13:34.63,Default,Eunuchs,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:37.64,Default,Gaoshun,0,0,0,,A steam bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.64,0:13:40.09,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,Apparently, sweating is good for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:41.75,Default,Gaoshun,0,0,0,,Is it useful?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.18,0:13:43.46,Default,Jinshi,0,0,0,,I suppose it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:47.18,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,We have to use whatever we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:13:59.72,Default,Lihua,0,0,0,,You... Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:03.26,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:08.23,Default,Lihua,0,0,0,,Why wouldn't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:13.08,Default,Lihua,0,0,0,,let me just die?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:18.08,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,You could stop eating, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:22.90,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,But you eat the porridge because you want to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:43.98,Default,Lihua,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:15:00.21,Default,Lihua,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.15,0:15:49.40,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.26,0:15:56.18,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 1,0,0,0,,I was released from confinement and am permitted to serve Lady Lihua once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:16:01.60,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 1,0,0,0,,I will never make that mistake again. Ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:06.44,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 1,0,0,0,,I will take your place now. Please rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:09.32,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:17.61,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 1,0,0,0,,Lady Lihua.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.93,0:16:23.34,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 1,0,0,0,,Lady Lihua.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:28.55,Default,Lihua,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:37.22,Default,Lihua,0,0,0,,Can you get me some water, if you could?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:42.57,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 1,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.93,0:16:47.74,Default,Lady-in-Waiting 1,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:59.56,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,After about two months, Lady Lihua recovered enough to be able to walk by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:06.10,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,She has self-respect, but isn't arrogant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:10.30,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,After that matter with the prince, I imagined her as a selfish princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.25,0:17:15.14,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,but as it turns out, she has a personality befitting a concubine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:53.83,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,I will take my leave tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:17:55.69,Default,Lihua,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.35,0:17:59.42,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,I've already spoken to your ladies-in-waiting about your food
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:01.40,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,and other things to be careful of.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:08.60,Default,Lihua,0,0,0,,Hey. Am I incapable of birthing another child?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.34,0:18:14.36,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,I don't know. Perhaps you should try.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.76,0:18:17.61,Default,Lihua,0,0,0,,But His Majesty's love for me is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.47,0:18:21.62,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,I was sent here by a direct order from the emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.21,0:18:27.78,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Once I return to the Jade Pavilion, perhaps the emperor will visit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.48,0:18:34.56,Default,Lihua,0,0,0,,I ignored those words of advice and let my child die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.56,0:18:36.78,Default,Lihua,0,0,0,,Will I be able to win against Concubine Gyokuyou?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:40.73,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,It's not a matter of winning and losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:45.55,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,There are hundreds, thousands of flowers in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:51.03,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,but who can decide whether a peony or a bellflower is more beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.08,0:18:56.18,Default,Lihua,0,0,0,,I have neither her jade eyes nor her bright hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.10,0:19:03.04,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,You have other... assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.31,0:19:09.41,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Not just the sheer size, but the shape and tension are truly magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:10.73,Default,Lihua,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.75,0:19:14.62,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Could you lend me your ear?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.62,0:19:16.17,Default,Lihua,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:33.30,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:42.17,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,The knowledge I left with Lady Lihua was a secret technique taught to me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.29,0:19:39.59,top,Lady-in-Waiting,0,0,0,,Lady Lihua, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.22,0:19:42.38,top,Ladies-in-Waiting,0,0,0,,Lady Lihua?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.17,0:19:43.49,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,by my big sisters at the brothel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.07,0:19:47.31,flashback,Pairin,0,0,0,,You should learn this, just in case!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.31,0:19:48.49,flashback,Young Maomao,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:54.60,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I don't have the sizable fruits to employ the technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:57.37,italics,Maomao,0,0,0,,It's perfect for Lady Lihua, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:01.70,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,I hope it turns out to be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:09.47,Default,Maomao,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:11.81,Default,Gyokuyou,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.28,0:20:14.23,Default,Yinghua,0,0,0,,Maomao, are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.68,0:20:16.48,Default,Guiyuan,0,0,0,,You've gotten so thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:18.72,Default,Ailan,0,0,0,,It must have been very hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.72,0:20:23.32,italics,Jinshi,0,0,0,,She completed the emperor's mission all by herself. Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.43,0:20:29.64,italics,Narration,0,0,0,,There was a period after that where the emperor's visits to the Jade Pavilion
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.64,0:20:32.30,italics,Narration,0,0,0,,decreased in frequency quite significantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:38.46,Default,Gyokuyou,0,0,0,,Finally, released from sleep deprivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.99,0:20:44.88,italics,Narration,0,0,0,,Maomao couldn't keep a straight face, but that's another story.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:02.03,Default,Eunuch,0,0,0,,It's a curse...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:50.05,Next_Time,Text,0,0,0,,Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.42,0:22:48.59,top,Narration,0,0,0,,Next time: "Covert Operations."
